  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will help us learn more about how maternal health can influence child health.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This study follows people who are healthy and less than 36 weeks pregnant to see how the
      mother's health can impact their child's growth and development. Up to 300 people including
      the mother and their future child will be a part of this study. The study will follow the
      child until they are two years of age.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
